00:13:23.799 --> 00:13:25.139
that which I also received,

00:13:25.139 --> 00:13:27.179
how that Christ died for our sins,

00:13:27.179 --> 00:13:28.339
according to the scriptures,

00:13:28.339 --> 00:13:29.779
and that he was buried,

00:13:29.779 --> 00:13:32.299
and that he rose again the third day,

00:13:32.299 --> 00:13:34.119
according to the scriptures.

00:13:34.119 --> 00:13:37.719
The gospel is the message that the world needs.

00:13:37.719 --> 00:13:40.379
Not politics, not my opinion,

00:13:40.379 --> 00:13:42.299
not the latest fashion statements

00:13:42.299 --> 00:13:44.259
or fashion whatever this, that, or the other thing.

00:13:44.259 --> 00:13:48.219
No, the message they need is the gospel.

00:13:48.219 --> 00:13:49.419
If I'm convinced of anything,

00:13:49.439 --> 00:13:51.359
we've been at the DC Gospel Outreach now,

00:13:51.359 --> 00:13:53.359
out on the streets for about two weeks now.

00:13:53.359 --> 00:13:55.759
