00:17:53.139 --> 00:17:56.139
The great commission is not an option to be considered.

00:17:56.139 --> 00:18:00.179
It is a command to be obeyed.

00:18:00.179 --> 00:18:03.219
Will we take Christ's command seriously to go into preach?

