00:23:42.739 --> 00:23:44.219
I'm just kind of shaking my head.

00:23:44.219 --> 00:23:45.399
I'm like, all right.

00:23:45.399 --> 00:23:47.339
So I was kind of feeling him out a little bit.

00:23:47.339 --> 00:23:49.619
